01:12:54,760 --> 01:12:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] najveći neprijatelj, dakle,

1542
01:12:55,840 --> 01:12:57,020
[SPEAKER_00] ugrožavaju vam život, jel?

1543
01:12:57,020 --> 01:12:59,239
[SPEAKER_00] S njima morate biti u kontaktu, jel?

1544
01:12:59,239 --> 01:13:00,939
[SPEAKER_00] A zapravo trebati distancije i tako dalje.

1545
01:13:01,399 --> 01:13:05,020
[SPEAKER_00] E, sad, tu se vidi ta temeljna razvojnost Hrvatske,

1546
01:13:05,020 --> 01:13:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Srbija je bila organizirana

1547
01:13:07,039 --> 01:13:09,220
[SPEAKER_00] u vrijeme srbijanske agresije

1548
01:13:09,220 --> 01:13:10,279
[SPEAKER_00] i ništa se nije promijenilo

1549
01:13:10,279 --> 01:13:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] i ova cijela operacija sa studentima,

1550
01:13:11,920 --> 01:13:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] po meni, po nekim tim gibljinih kriterijima,

1551
01:13:13,920 --> 01:13:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] studenti su, dakle, najuporniji neudustaju

1552
01:13:17,340 --> 01:13:19,819
[SPEAKER_00] i zna se, to su sve stručne i znanstvene procjene,

1553
01:13:19,819 --> 01:13:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] za razliku, ne znam, od odrastih radnika,

1554
01:13:22,079 --> 01:13:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] nastavnika, medicinara,

1555
01:13:23,579 --> 01:13:27,939
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, sudaca ili djelatnika pravosudije i tako dalje,

1556
01:13:28,300 --> 01:13:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] oni imaju odriženu i fizičku i drugačiju,

1557
01:13:30,239 --> 01:13:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, mentalnu izdržljivost,

1558
01:13:31,460 --> 01:13:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, adaptibilniji su, ovaj,

1559
01:13:33,420 --> 01:13:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] lakše će se prilagoditi na trpljenje, slično,

1560
01:13:35,340 --> 01:13:37,819
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad mladi klenu, njih je nemoguće zaustaviti,

1561
01:13:37,819 --> 01:13:39,680
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je ta operacija vrlo dobro vođena

1562
01:13:39,680 --> 01:13:41,979
[SPEAKER_00] i da tu vode srbijanske službe,

1563
01:13:41,979 --> 01:13:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] isto tako...

1564
01:13:45,079 --> 01:13:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Mislite prosvjede studenta ta?

1565
01:13:46,920 --> 01:13:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] Službe, ali na linku, dakle, i sa Moskvom,

1566
01:13:49,880 --> 01:13:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] da ne ulazimo sad u cijelu tu elaboraciju

1567
01:13:53,619 --> 01:13:56,039
[SPEAKER_00] i to će ići do kraja, jer mladi neće odustajati,

1568
01:13:56,159 --> 01:13:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] priključivačenice i roditelji koji su,

1569
01:13:58,079 --> 01:14:00,439
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, ili solidarno sa mladima

1570
01:14:00,439 --> 01:14:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] i uvijek postoji ta stvonost, tako da...

1571
01:14:02,659 --> 01:14:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] A cilje je rušenje Aleksandra Vučića?

1572
01:14:04,880 --> 01:14:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, cilje je uvijek kad ide treba rušiti,

1573
01:14:07,579 --> 01:14:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, puno je sanemljivih par,

1574
01:14:09,039 --> 01:14:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, vi ste kod dolazi, jel, dakle...

1575
01:14:10,800 --> 01:14:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, imaš li neko...

1576
01:14:12,239 --> 01:14:14,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, neko ko ruši, on zapravo puno više,

1577
01:14:14,340 --> 01:14:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] jer vidi da će srušiti, dakle, Vučiće morat otići,

1578
01:14:17,079 --> 01:14:18,560
[SPEAKER_00] iako žrtvuje figure, ovaj,

1579
01:14:18,560 --> 01:14:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] više nego Plenković,

1580
01:14:19,619 --> 01:14:20,979
[SPEAKER_00] jo, Plenković je doći u tu fazu,

1581
01:14:20,979 --> 01:14:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] jo, kad će i to pokušati,

1582
01:14:22,420 --> 01:14:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali kako smo mi u tom kontroliranom kaosu,

1583
01:14:25,539 --> 01:14:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] bit će drugačije.

1584
01:14:27,279 --> 01:14:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] To znači, Vučiće morat otići,

1585
01:14:30,500 --> 01:14:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam rekao,

1586
01:14:31,220 --> 01:14:32,779
[SPEAKER_00] zanimljivo, kad je bilo,

1587
01:14:32,779 --> 01:14:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] to sam, mislim, negdje javno komentiruo,

1588
01:14:34,699 --> 01:14:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] ali pogotovo sa prijateljima,

1589
01:14:35,760 --> 01:14:37,520
[SPEAKER_00] kad on nije otišao na BRICS,

1590
01:14:37,520 --> 01:14:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] a pozvan je jedini dva mjeseca rani,

1591
01:14:39,260 --> 01:14:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam rekao, on je ušao u Džinđičevo prostor,

1592
01:14:41,340 --> 01:14:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] znači, bilo fizički ili politički mora otići, ne?

1593
01:14:44,720 --> 01:14:46,600
[SPEAKER_01] Da, potpisao si je nešto.

1594
01:14:46,600 --> 01:14:50,060
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ste opet spomenuli malo premijera Plenkovića,

1595
01:14:50,060 --> 01:14:52,939
[SPEAKER_01] što mislite, zašto je on promijenio retoriku oko Rusije?

1596
01:14:52,939 --> 01:14:56,060
[SPEAKER_00] Pa on je, on je...

1597
01:14:56,060 --> 01:14:57,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ono kao treba se pretopregovarati.

1598
01:14:57,359 --> 01:14:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja sam fasciniran koliko on ništa ne zna.

1599
01:14:59,800 --> 01:15:02,479
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, on je, evo, idem, on je, dakle,

1600
01:15:02,479 --> 01:15:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] mlađi čovjek i usporediv sa Milanovićem,

1601
01:15:05,079 --> 01:15:08,600
[SPEAKER_00] evo, dakle, na neke načine generacije su,

1602
01:15:08,600 --> 01:15:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] pa bili su bliski, maljski poslovi, očevi itd.

1603
01:15:13,880 --> 01:15:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] Zaista je neprosjećni apsolutisti, jel?

1604
01:15:15,920 --> 01:15:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] To sve je u odnosu prema...

1605
01:15:18,079 --> 01:15:20,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, on je postavljen za nekakvog glavnog povjerenika

1606
01:15:20,760 --> 01:15:22,180
[SPEAKER_00] za pitanja ukrajine slišala.

1607
01:15:22,180 --> 01:15:23,939
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, toliko puta je izručio Hrvatsku,

1608
01:15:23,939 --> 01:15:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] možete misliti, pamet nekakog u izručnoj vlasti,

1609
01:15:27,619 --> 01:15:29,319
[SPEAKER_00] koji kaže, mi smo proporcionalno,

1610
01:15:29,319 --> 01:15:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno proizvodnika BDP,

1611
01:15:30,579 --> 01:15:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] najviše pomogli Ukrajini.

1612
01:15:32,199 --> 01:15:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, 300 milijuna, ne znam, ova, eura, dolara smo.

1613
01:15:34,920 --> 01:15:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže, od toga 200 milijuna, ovo je oružja,

1614
01:15:37,579 --> 01:15:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je streljiva itd.

1615
01:15:38,659 --> 01:15:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Što to znači? On je 6,5 tona,

1616
01:15:40,800 --> 01:15:43,439
[SPEAKER_00] nigdje nije doletio, prazda vam, raketa,

1617
01:15:43,439 --> 01:15:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] nego nama.

1618
01:15:44,460 --> 01:15:46,300
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo...

1619
01:15:46,300 --> 01:15:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] A vi još dajte.

1620
01:15:47,079 --> 01:15:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da, idu neki narati, pa to je slučajno,

1621
01:15:49,119 --> 01:15:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] pa to je ovo, to je ono.

1622
01:15:50,140 --> 01:15:50,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nema slučajnosti.

1623
01:15:50,859 --> 01:15:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nema slučajnosti, tako da on siroće, rekao bih, luta,

1624
01:15:54,380 --> 01:15:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali ta izgubjenost se može vidjeti,

1625
01:15:55,920 --> 01:15:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] on je odgojan pod tim staklenim zvonom.

1626
01:15:58,000 --> 01:16:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] Možete misliti takvog mlađeg lika,

1627
01:16:01,340 --> 01:16:04,100
[SPEAKER_00] da on, čini mi se, matronom bavi se Kardeljem.

1628
01:16:04,100 --> 01:16:09,100
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Kardeljem je bio smiješan klincima njegovog naraštaja tada.

1629
01:16:09,100 --> 01:16:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su, ne znam, bavi se...

1630
01:16:10,779 --> 01:16:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] A i tko zna za Edvarda Kardelja, ono, više, jel?

1631
01:16:13,659 --> 01:16:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je tata pisao komunikacijski,

1632
01:16:17,239 --> 01:16:23,979
[SPEAKER_00] po onom obrazu, dakle, odnosno, stranka ili grupacija

1633
01:16:23,979 --> 01:16:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] koja ima vlast, ona, dakle, manipulacija,

1634
01:16:26,800 --> 01:16:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] jedna agit-prokovska zastavljena definicija.

1635
01:16:29,380 --> 01:16:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] On se dalje od toga, nažalost, nije maknulo,

1636
01:16:31,739 --> 01:16:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] a drugo, vidi se ta neprostičnja da se okružuje,

1637
01:16:34,760 --> 01:16:38,100
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, sa osobama, dakle, pre neiskusnima,

1638
01:16:38,100 --> 01:16:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] pre bez integriteta i slično,

1639
01:16:40,279 --> 01:16:42,899
[SPEAKER_00] umjesto da je za svaki sektor odobrao cijeli niz

1640
01:16:42,899 --> 01:16:44,979
[SPEAKER_00] vrhunskih slušnjaka koji ima Hrvatska.

1641
01:16:44,979 --> 01:16:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, za sva područja, kad kaže se nema ljudi,

1642
01:16:47,239 --> 01:16:49,020
[SPEAKER_00] ja ono isto, ovo, najviše sjedim,

1643
01:16:49,020 --> 01:16:50,779
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ja kažem, uđite u travaj,

1644
01:16:50,779 --> 01:16:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] naćete bolji sastav nego što je Plenković odobrao.

1645
01:16:54,960 --> 01:16:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] Tu su razni komplekci, dakle, socijalne,

1646
01:16:56,800 --> 01:16:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] manje, nacionalne vrijednosti.

1647
01:16:58,119 --> 01:17:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] Moglo bi se o njemu elaborirati, koliko hoćete,

1648
01:17:01,659 --> 01:17:03,439
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad, kad ta balon se ispuhao,

1649
01:17:03,439 --> 01:17:04,380
[SPEAKER_00] to će sad, ovaj,

1650
01:17:04,380 --> 01:17:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] to će sad biti zanimljivo pratiti.

1651
01:17:07,180 --> 01:17:07,899
[SPEAKER_00] To boga, ne, da.

1652
01:17:07,899 --> 01:17:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] Što mislite, kakva sudbina čeka Dodika?

1653
01:17:10,800 --> 01:17:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] Čini se nekako da on gleda

1654
01:17:13,159 --> 01:17:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] s velikim očima i prema Trumpu

1655
01:17:15,239 --> 01:17:17,640
[SPEAKER_01] i prema Putinu? Pa, Dodigo je jasno,

1656
01:17:17,640 --> 01:17:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, da je on isturen,

1657
01:17:19,539 --> 01:17:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] tako da je nekada, u vrijeme

1658
01:17:21,340 --> 01:17:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] Osmanlija, bosanski pašaluk je bio

1659
01:17:23,319 --> 01:17:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] utvrda, s kojim se urišali na Beć,

1660
01:17:25,079 --> 01:17:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] išli do Poljske, dakle, i...

1661
01:17:26,859 --> 01:17:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] To je bila baza. Da, to je bila baza, tako da je on

1662
01:17:29,279 --> 01:17:30,939
[SPEAKER_00] svjestan da je baza.

1663
01:17:30,939 --> 01:17:32,720
[SPEAKER_00] S druge strane,

1664
01:17:32,720 --> 01:17:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] kad se pojavio mladi Staniv Guković,

1665
01:17:34,880 --> 01:17:36,520
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam baš pisala jedan tekst o tome,

1666
01:17:36,520 --> 01:17:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] analizirajući njega i nešto istražajući,

1667
01:17:38,420 --> 01:17:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je još gore ako dođe

1668
01:17:41,000 --> 01:17:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj Staniv Guković, dakle, mladi dečko,

1669
01:17:45,239 --> 01:17:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] Miloševićem i slično, jel, sad dogi on se zna

1670
01:17:47,779 --> 01:17:49,760
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, gdje je, i on je potpuno

1671
01:17:49,760 --> 01:17:51,859
[SPEAKER_00] transparentan, jel, zna ko stoji

1672
01:17:51,859 --> 01:17:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] iza njega, jel,

1673
01:17:52,659 --> 01:17:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] zna se da, ovaj, ne znam,

1674
01:17:55,199 --> 01:17:57,520
[SPEAKER_00] supersila SAD neće uću,

1675
01:17:57,520 --> 01:17:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, atomske sile, među sobom,

1676
01:17:59,199 --> 01:18:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] teško da će, ovaj,

1677
01:18:01,859 --> 01:18:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] jedna protiv druge zaraditi,

1678
01:18:03,579 --> 01:18:04,979
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek će to završiti na nekoj, ovaj,

1679
01:18:04,979 --> 01:18:07,359
[SPEAKER_00] na nekoj trgovini ili preko nečijih leđa, jel.

1680
01:18:08,159 --> 01:18:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] E, i on je tu, što bih rekao, ovaj,

1681
01:18:10,300 --> 01:18:12,680
[SPEAKER_00] transparentan, poluzdan,

1682
01:18:12,680 --> 01:18:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] i svi znaju, ovaj,

1683
01:18:14,260 --> 01:18:16,439
[SPEAKER_00] kapacitete i slično, jel,

1684
01:18:16,439 --> 01:18:18,060
[SPEAKER_00] pa režu mu ove neke krakove,

1685
01:18:18,060 --> 01:18:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali puno su opasni, jasno, to isto,

1686
01:18:20,180 --> 01:18:21,939
[SPEAKER_00] kad su Amerikan, kad se Blinken spustio,

1687
01:18:21,939 --> 01:18:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] ono sam, to me nešto pisao, ovaj, eto,

1688
01:18:23,840 --> 01:18:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] možda neko pročita,

1689
01:18:25,899 --> 01:18:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] kada je ono bilo 50 dodikovih,

1690
01:18:28,039 --> 01:18:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, će, uve sancija, kažem,

1691
01:18:29,699 --> 01:18:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] to nema nikakvog smisla, jer dodik je potpuno jasan,

1692
01:18:32,119 --> 01:18:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] ali i svi drugi, to znači, Čović, Komšić i Izet, Begović, mladi,

1693
01:18:35,760 --> 01:18:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] jednako služe Beogradu,

1694
01:18:37,680 --> 01:18:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] samo se osisirani,

1695
01:18:38,539 --> 01:18:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] ako neko hoće integrirati u Beogradu,

1696
01:18:40,039 --> 01:18:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] onda mora, barem svih, svakome od njih,

1697
01:18:42,420 --> 01:18:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] 50 ovih glavnih srezati.

1698
01:18:44,539 --> 01:18:45,680
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, to se ne događa

1699
01:18:45,680 --> 01:18:48,060
[SPEAKER_00] i tu su najveći stranali svi, dakle, Hrvati,

1700
01:18:48,060 --> 01:18:49,600
[SPEAKER_00] jesu ta od svega toga, ne.

1701
01:18:49,600 --> 01:18:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, a što mislite, kako će dodik završiti?

1702
01:18:52,159 --> 01:18:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] Drma mu se sad,

1703
01:18:54,659 --> 01:18:55,880
[SPEAKER_01] evo sad je onaj sviče, skoro.

1704
01:18:56,239 --> 01:18:57,819
[SPEAKER_00] Pa pitanje, ko će ga zamijeniti, jel?

1705
01:18:57,819 --> 01:18:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, uvijek se ovaj...

1706
01:18:59,340 --> 01:19:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nego, kova će naći,

1707
01:19:00,880 --> 01:19:02,239
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi ga zamijeniti.

1708
01:19:02,239 --> 01:19:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kova će naći, ali on je najpouzdaniji ima,

1709
01:19:04,199 --> 01:19:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, on je već okoštao.

1710
01:19:06,359 --> 01:19:08,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ima strukturu, to znači,

1711
01:19:08,100 --> 01:19:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] i vojnu, i policijsku,

1712
01:19:11,140 --> 01:19:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] a da ne govorimo ovo,

1713
01:19:12,180 --> 01:19:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što se gospodarsku,

1714
01:19:14,960 --> 01:19:16,439
[SPEAKER_00] što bi široko rekla.

1715
01:19:16,439 --> 01:19:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ima strukturu,

1716
01:19:17,300 --> 01:19:19,140
[SPEAKER_00] bez infrastrukture,

1717
01:19:19,140 --> 01:19:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] ne možete tamo ući,

1718
01:19:20,960 --> 01:19:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] on je to etnički očistio

1719
01:19:22,899 --> 01:19:24,859
[SPEAKER_00] i to je Slobodan Milošević,

1720
01:19:24,939 --> 01:19:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji je iznimno obrazovan bio.

1721
01:19:26,340 --> 01:19:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio najpotencijalniji mladi bankar

1722
01:19:28,739 --> 01:19:29,319
[SPEAKER_00] u Jugoslaviji,

1723
01:19:29,319 --> 01:19:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] prije nego su ga doveli,

1724
01:19:30,399 --> 01:19:32,600
[SPEAKER_00] bio nekoliko desetaka puta u Americi

1725
01:19:32,600 --> 01:19:34,819
[SPEAKER_00] i svako može otići na još uvijek

1726
01:19:34,819 --> 01:19:37,260
[SPEAKER_00] haški sud, pa pogledati,

1727
01:19:37,260 --> 01:19:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, njego perfektni engleski znanje prava,

1728
01:19:39,500 --> 01:19:40,779
[SPEAKER_00] znanje ekonomije,

1729
01:19:40,779 --> 01:19:42,479
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, bolji od svih odjetnika tamo, jel?

1730
01:19:42,479 --> 01:19:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1731
01:19:43,399 --> 01:19:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] priča nije jednostavna, jel?

1732
01:19:48,079 --> 01:19:49,680
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je mi hoćemo banalizirati,

1733
01:19:49,680 --> 01:19:51,140
[SPEAKER_00] sve je poznato,

1734
01:19:51,140 --> 01:19:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad imate neprosvjećene ljude

1735
01:19:53,359 --> 01:19:54,479
[SPEAKER_00] na ključnim mjestima, jel?

1736
01:19:54,939 --> 01:19:56,319
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo bez uši u oči,

1737
01:19:56,319 --> 01:19:58,520
[SPEAKER_00] a onda kako možete donositi odluke,

1738
01:19:58,520 --> 01:19:59,979
[SPEAKER_00] a pogotovo ovog ranga,

1739
01:19:59,979 --> 01:20:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je Palenković,

1740
01:20:01,279 --> 01:20:01,399
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

1741
01:20:01,399 --> 01:20:02,520
[SPEAKER_00] Potpuno iznudjen čovjek.

1742
01:20:02,520 --> 01:20:05,279
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto sam vam spitala za Dodika?

1743
01:20:05,279 --> 01:20:07,180
[SPEAKER_01] Naime, ministar Anušić ovdje je rekao

1744
01:20:07,180 --> 01:20:10,100
[SPEAKER_01] da su najvrućije točke

1745
01:20:10,100 --> 01:20:11,159
[SPEAKER_01] ovog dijela Evrope,

1746
01:20:11,159 --> 01:20:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] Bosna i Hercegovina i Kosovo.

1747
01:20:13,220 --> 01:20:14,600
[SPEAKER_01] s druge strane Hrvatska se naoružava.

1748
01:20:14,600 --> 01:20:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] Neko su toliko?

1749
01:20:15,340 --> 01:20:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, to ja sam sad njega citirala.

1750
01:20:17,880 --> 01:20:19,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam sad njega citirala.

1751
01:20:19,479 --> 01:20:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] U njoj je najveća vatra, jel?

1752
01:20:21,779 --> 01:20:23,680
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zemlja NATO koja je izvučena,

1753
01:20:23,680 --> 01:20:24,520
[SPEAKER_00] iskljena NATO,

1754
01:20:24,520 --> 01:20:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] ali sa odobrenjem Amerikana.

1755
01:20:25,880 --> 01:20:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tada kad se dogodio desat,

1756
01:20:28,060 --> 01:20:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] Porfirija i Joannike,

1757
01:20:30,140 --> 01:20:31,859
[SPEAKER_00] sa NATO-vnim helikopterom,

1758
01:20:31,859 --> 01:20:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, jer Crnogorska policija

1759
01:20:34,239 --> 01:20:35,260
[SPEAKER_00] nije htjela dati svoj,

1760
01:20:35,260 --> 01:20:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego je Crnogorska vojska dala.

1761
01:20:36,960 --> 01:20:38,640
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su, dakle, isto tako u NATO, jel?

1762
01:20:38,640 --> 01:20:41,600
[SPEAKER_00] Američko verposlanstvo je dalo

1763
01:20:41,600 --> 01:20:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] jednu pomidljivu javnu izjavu,

1764
01:20:47,220 --> 01:20:49,779
[SPEAKER_00] govoreći da vlast ne bude previše gruba,

1765
01:20:49,779 --> 01:20:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] a prosvjednike mole da budu dobri, ne?

1766
01:20:51,739 --> 01:20:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] A izvlače im iz vlasti, jel?

1767
01:20:54,079 --> 01:20:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] U toj trgovini globalnoj,

1768
01:20:55,420 --> 01:20:57,800
[SPEAKER_00] zemlju koja je već bila dvije, tri godine u NATO.

1769
01:20:57,800 --> 01:20:59,640
[SPEAKER_01] Da se samo malo vratimo.

1770
01:20:59,640 --> 01:21:02,020
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on je spomenuo Kosovo i BiH

1771
01:21:02,020 --> 01:21:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] kao najvruće točke.

1772
01:21:03,420 --> 01:21:04,600
[SPEAKER_01] S druge strane,

1773
01:21:04,600 --> 01:21:07,619
[SPEAKER_01] nadovezala sam se Hrvatska se naoružava,

1774
01:21:07,619 --> 01:21:10,399
[SPEAKER_01] ne naoružavamo se da bismo lovili leptire.

1775
01:21:10,399 --> 01:21:12,899
[SPEAKER_01] Jasno je kao dan.

1776
01:21:12,899 --> 01:21:15,340
[SPEAKER_01] Govorili ste o tome kako će nas muka nadjirati.

1777
01:21:15,340 --> 01:21:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, moji prigovor je,

1778
01:21:16,539 --> 01:21:18,340
[SPEAKER_00] da, i Plinković je najprije,

1779
01:21:18,340 --> 01:21:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] evo, u zadnjem mome,

1780
01:21:19,340 --> 01:21:20,100
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, tom,

1781
01:21:20,100 --> 01:21:21,859
[SPEAKER_00] aktualstvo,

1782
01:21:21,859 --> 01:21:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam je opravljeno dvije minute,

1783
01:21:22,899 --> 01:21:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] ili minutu, ne zna šta je bila replika,

1784
01:21:24,920 --> 01:21:26,939
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam rekao da je razružao Hrvatsko.

1785
01:21:26,939 --> 01:21:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] on se, rekao bih, onako, naivno,

1786
01:21:29,039 --> 01:21:30,060
[SPEAKER_00] kod djete raspometio,

1787
01:21:30,060 --> 01:21:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] misliš da je to glupost, ne.

1788
01:21:31,539 --> 01:21:34,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sam navio da je izručio sve oružje,

1789
01:21:34,060 --> 01:21:35,720
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatsko, koje imamo,

1790
01:21:35,720 --> 01:21:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] znači, uključujući te 84,

1791
01:21:37,079 --> 01:21:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] da ne govorim sve promiđbene,

1792
01:21:38,819 --> 01:21:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, za onaj naš više cijelni

1793
01:21:40,539 --> 01:21:42,640
[SPEAKER_00] bacač i tako dalje.

1794
01:21:43,760 --> 01:21:46,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, izručili smo svoje postojeće oružje,

1795
01:21:46,300 --> 01:21:47,060
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam,

1796
01:21:47,060 --> 01:21:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, u vojnom smislu,

1797
01:21:48,920 --> 01:21:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] nismo ne znam što i to je,

1798
01:21:50,119 --> 01:21:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] to se čak predsjednik države to rekao,

1799
01:21:52,739 --> 01:21:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] jel, javno,

1800
01:21:53,319 --> 01:21:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] i što je više manje točno,

1801
01:21:55,680 --> 01:21:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] a naručili smo oružje koje će doći

1802
01:21:58,399 --> 01:22:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] možda za pet godina,

1803
01:22:00,079 --> 01:22:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] jel, u tih pet godina dogodit će se,

1804
01:22:02,000 --> 01:22:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] a već trajeti,

1805
01:22:03,220 --> 01:22:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] čirni ćemo se mi braniti,

1806
01:22:04,319 --> 01:22:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] opet ću se vratiti na ministra.

1807
01:22:05,779 --> 01:22:07,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, dakle, s jedne strane,

1808
01:22:07,060 --> 01:22:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, dali smo oružje koje imamo,

1809
01:22:09,460 --> 01:22:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] a dobić kupili smo nekakvo evo oružje.

1810
01:22:11,739 --> 01:22:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je baš bilo,

1811
01:22:12,760 --> 01:22:13,939
[SPEAKER_00] kad je bilo za Himarse,

1812
01:22:13,939 --> 01:22:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] naravno da je to vrlo kvalitno oružje,

1813
01:22:15,739 --> 01:22:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] a smo kupili rakete,

1814
01:22:18,300 --> 01:22:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] to znači stredljivo,

1815
01:22:19,279 --> 01:22:21,439
[SPEAKER_00] dometa 80 kilometara.

1816
01:22:21,439 --> 01:22:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam o tom imao žestoku rašplu,

1817
01:22:23,119 --> 01:22:24,100
[SPEAKER_00] nisam mogo dobiti odgovor.

1818
01:22:24,100 --> 01:22:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto nismo kupili 300 ili 500

1819
01:22:25,739 --> 01:22:27,020
[SPEAKER_00] ako idemo na odvraćanje, jel?

1820
01:22:27,380 --> 01:22:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kome ćemo mi pjetiti sa 80 kilometara,

1821
01:22:29,380 --> 01:22:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] Koprivnici, Karlovcu, Sisku, jel?

1822
01:22:31,500 --> 01:22:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] A zna se da u našem okruženju,

1823
01:22:33,619 --> 01:22:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, smo u NATO okruženju,

1824
01:22:35,180 --> 01:22:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, nekakvom prijateljskom,

1825
01:22:36,420 --> 01:22:39,560
[SPEAKER_00] jedino Srbija i Republika Srpska

1826
01:22:39,560 --> 01:22:41,859
[SPEAKER_00] su, dakle, nekoga koga trebamo odvaćati.

1827
01:22:41,859 --> 01:22:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] Poprašit ćemo,

1828
01:22:42,619 --> 01:22:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] Beogra ćemo poprašiti sa raketama

1829
01:22:45,079 --> 01:22:45,899
[SPEAKER_00] koje mogu dojti do,

1830
01:22:45,899 --> 01:22:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] tu do Novske, do Kutina, jel?

1831
01:22:47,579 --> 01:22:49,979
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, puno toga je,

1832
01:22:49,979 --> 01:22:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] puno toga je problematično, jel?

1833
01:22:52,420 --> 01:22:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam čak postavljao pitanje,

1834
01:22:54,220 --> 01:22:55,140
[SPEAKER_00] zanima me koje je,

1835
01:22:55,140 --> 01:22:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] uopće osmišljavao tu strategiju, jel?

1836
01:22:57,619 --> 01:22:59,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu zamisliti da neki vojni stručnak

1837
01:22:59,439 --> 01:23:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] govori o odvraćanju, jel?

1838
01:23:01,199 --> 01:23:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kao to je stručna ekipa, jel?

1839
01:23:04,039 --> 01:23:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nekakav, jel, uvijek idete u...

1840
01:23:06,500 --> 01:23:07,520
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nema pojedinca,

1841
01:23:07,520 --> 01:23:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] nego nekakav kolektivitet, jel odgovor.

1842
01:23:09,319 --> 01:23:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] Je li ti ga povjerenstvo?

1843
01:23:10,159 --> 01:23:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je poznato.

1844
01:23:11,000 --> 01:23:12,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ako želiš neći problem,

1845
01:23:12,399 --> 01:23:14,060
[SPEAKER_00] osnovi povjerenstvo, jel?

1846
01:23:14,060 --> 01:23:15,560
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, dakle, da je nezamisljivo

1847
01:23:15,560 --> 01:23:16,060
[SPEAKER_00] da neko...

1848
01:23:16,060 --> 01:23:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je onda pitanje namjera,

1849
01:23:17,279 --> 01:23:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne struke, dakle,

1850
01:23:18,079 --> 01:23:19,760
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da obični vojnik zna,

1851
01:23:19,760 --> 01:23:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj,

1852
01:23:20,140 --> 01:23:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] dosad 80 ne može nikoga,

1853
01:23:22,699 --> 01:23:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, pogotovo Srbiju, odvraćati, jel?

1854
01:23:24,579 --> 01:23:25,819
[SPEAKER_00] Da, koja je...

1855
01:23:25,819 --> 01:23:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je možeš sugerirati napadnina, jel?

1856
01:23:27,880 --> 01:23:30,439
[SPEAKER_01] Koja je, kad ste ju sad već spomenuli,

1857
01:23:30,439 --> 01:23:33,319
[SPEAKER_01] puno prije i puno žešće se naoružava

1858
01:23:33,319 --> 01:23:34,520
[SPEAKER_01] nego mi?

1859
01:23:34,520 --> 01:23:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne govorimo o francuskih zaklopovih,

1860
01:23:36,340 --> 01:23:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja generacija,

1861
01:23:37,000 --> 01:23:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] a Srbija je kupila...

1862
01:23:39,079 --> 01:23:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] Puno bolje.

1863
01:23:39,640 --> 01:23:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] I tako dalje, i tako dalje, i tako dalje.

1864
01:23:41,579 --> 01:23:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, puno, puno toga je upitno

1865
01:23:43,399 --> 01:23:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] i ono, vraćamo se na početak emisije,

1866
01:23:46,239 --> 01:23:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, stvarno smo ovaj,

1867
01:23:47,960 --> 01:23:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, vele izdaje, diktatura

1868
01:23:50,659 --> 01:23:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] i sve što smo rekli,

1869
01:23:51,579 --> 01:23:55,020
[SPEAKER_00] možda na prvi pogled zvuči grubo,

1870
01:23:55,020 --> 01:23:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad ovo sve čak u emisiji

1871
01:23:56,699 --> 01:23:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] ovako na brzaka nabrojimo,

1872
01:23:58,079 --> 01:24:00,699
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da onda ne možete zapravo

1873
01:24:00,699 --> 01:24:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] vidjeti da su i to blage riječi.

1874
01:24:02,500 --> 01:24:03,319
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1875
01:24:03,319 --> 01:24:04,979
[SPEAKER_00] Nema reakcija odgovarajući.

1876
01:24:04,979 --> 01:24:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] Znači da su institucije zajedne,

1877
01:24:06,840 --> 01:24:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] imali ste doktora Milanovića,

1878
01:24:08,159 --> 01:24:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, i mnoge druge politologije

1879
01:24:10,539 --> 01:24:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] i slično, dakle, zarobljena država,

1880
01:24:12,159 --> 01:24:13,779
[SPEAKER_00] okupirane institucije,

1881
01:24:13,779 --> 01:24:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] u punom smislu se to može vidjeti,

1882
01:24:15,920 --> 01:24:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] na primjer, u Hrvatski.

1883
01:24:16,819 --> 01:24:19,899
[SPEAKER_01] Mislite li vi, evo, sada će uskoro

1884
01:24:19,899 --> 01:24:22,220
[SPEAKER_01] predsjednik Milanović dati po drugi puta

1885
01:24:22,220 --> 01:24:23,739
[SPEAKER_01] prisegu novih pet godina,

1886
01:24:23,739 --> 01:24:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] da dolaze vremena kada bi čak i Zoran Milanović

1887
01:24:28,460 --> 01:24:30,420
[SPEAKER_01] mogao obući odoru?

1888
01:24:30,420 --> 01:24:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] Već je jedan put skakao sa onog borbenog vozila,

1889
01:24:34,699 --> 01:24:35,640
[SPEAKER_00] pa mislim da ne bi ovo.

1890
01:24:36,300 --> 01:24:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, izvaćate me, dakle,

1891
01:24:38,079 --> 01:24:39,439
[SPEAKER_01] da dolaze vremena muke?

1892
01:24:39,439 --> 01:24:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, dolaze vremena, dakle,

1893
01:24:41,880 --> 01:24:43,060
[SPEAKER_00] ako gledamo tradiciju,

1894
01:24:43,060 --> 01:24:45,720
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je zaista turbulentan prostor.

1895
01:24:45,720 --> 01:24:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] To znači, uvijek su se tu ukrštali

1896
01:24:47,539 --> 01:24:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] svjetske geopolitike,

1897
01:24:49,199 --> 01:24:50,680
[SPEAKER_00] svjetski svjetonazori,

1898
01:24:50,680 --> 01:24:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] svjetske religije.

1899
01:24:52,119 --> 01:24:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] To je tisutljećima,

1900
01:24:54,399 --> 01:24:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] možemo pratiti.

1901
01:24:55,659 --> 01:24:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je jednako tako i danas,

1902
01:24:58,039 --> 01:25:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] i rijetko je prošlo nekoliko desetljeća,

1903
01:25:02,300 --> 01:25:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] a da tu nije došlo do oružanog sukova.

1904
01:25:04,359 --> 01:25:07,279
[SPEAKER_00] S time da mislim da Kosovo je,

1905
01:25:07,279 --> 01:25:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je Srbija ima dovoljno znanja,

1906
01:25:10,380 --> 01:25:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] da je Kosovo neporodno izgubila,

1907
01:25:12,640 --> 01:25:14,199
[SPEAKER_00] jer ga je izgubila demografski,

1908
01:25:14,199 --> 01:25:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] a Albanci i njihova kultura su sasvim drugačiji,

1909
01:25:18,079 --> 01:25:19,439
[SPEAKER_00] drugačiji i tako dalje.

1910
01:25:19,439 --> 01:25:20,020
[SPEAKER_00] I njima je to...

1911
01:25:20,020 --> 01:25:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] Oni nemaju demografski pad.

1912
01:25:20,819 --> 01:25:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] Oni imaju vrstu demografsku školu

1913
01:25:22,739 --> 01:25:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] već od 19. stojeća.

1914
01:25:23,880 --> 01:25:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je...

1915
01:25:25,260 --> 01:25:27,520
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, njih zanima Bosna i Hercegovina

1916
01:25:27,520 --> 01:25:29,720
[SPEAKER_00] i Hrvatska, gdje imaju uporišta.

1917
01:25:29,720 --> 01:25:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] Oni na Kosovo nemaju što tražiti,

1918
01:25:31,159 --> 01:25:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] to je jasno.

1919
01:25:31,659 --> 01:25:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je blef da istrguju nešto drugo,

1920
01:25:33,619 --> 01:25:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] rekao bih, pojednostavljeno.

1921
01:25:34,920 --> 01:25:37,560
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je nama najvažnija,

1922
01:25:37,560 --> 01:25:39,100
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, BH, Republika Srpska

1923
01:25:39,100 --> 01:25:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] je u Hrvatskom trguhu,

1924
01:25:40,199 --> 01:25:42,680
[SPEAKER_00] a mi imamo tih,

1925
01:25:42,859 --> 01:25:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] ali dobit ćemo.

1926
01:25:43,800 --> 01:25:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] Jesu li na Mađari opasni?

1927
01:25:45,380 --> 01:25:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, Mađari nisu opasni,

1928
01:25:47,000 --> 01:25:50,060
[SPEAKER_00] već zanimljio je da je njima nuđio...

1929
01:25:50,060 --> 01:25:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] Hitler im je nudio u raznim kombinacijama.

1930
01:25:52,359 --> 01:25:54,140
[SPEAKER_00] Tek na kraju je došlo na red Pavelić,

1931
01:25:54,140 --> 01:25:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] jer je Hitler isto imao vrlo dobru matematiku,

1932
01:25:56,279 --> 01:25:57,479
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, vrhunske strušnjake,

1933
01:25:57,479 --> 01:26:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] i doktrina Britskriga koja je britarska,

1934
01:26:00,199 --> 01:26:01,560
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, on ju je primijenio i tako dalje.

1935
01:26:01,560 --> 01:26:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] On je nudio, znajući šta ima,

1936
01:26:03,159 --> 01:26:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] par sto uštaša, jel, ovaj,

1937
01:26:04,420 --> 01:26:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] da ih je volio ili nije,

1938
01:26:05,779 --> 01:26:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] i Mađarima i tako dalje,

1939
01:26:08,380 --> 01:26:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] da preuzimo odgovornost,

1940
01:26:10,119 --> 01:26:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] jer su imali infrastrukturu,

1941
01:26:11,039 --> 01:26:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mađari su odustali od toga.

1942
01:26:12,239 --> 01:26:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je toga i ranije.

1943
01:26:13,659 --> 01:26:16,439
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Mađari su nakav raspada austrugarske,

1944
01:26:16,439 --> 01:26:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] ako imaju neke ambicije,

1945
01:26:19,220 --> 01:26:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] mogu imati prema Vojvodini,

1946
01:26:20,319 --> 01:26:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] mogu to na nekim rumunjskim dijelovima,

1947
01:26:21,800 --> 01:26:22,520
[SPEAKER_00] da sad ne ulazimo,

1948
01:26:22,520 --> 01:26:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali prema Hrvatskoj ne,

1949
01:26:24,000 --> 01:26:25,399
[SPEAKER_00] oni se prema Hrvatskoj ponašaju

1950
01:26:25,399 --> 01:26:27,520
[SPEAKER_00] kao suvremeni imperi,

1951
01:26:27,520 --> 01:26:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] znači kapitalom i na drugi način,

1952
01:26:29,340 --> 01:26:32,640
[SPEAKER_00] oni već od nekih uporišta na Jadranskoj obali

1953
01:26:32,640 --> 01:26:33,399
[SPEAKER_00] do, ne znam,

1954
01:26:35,779 --> 01:26:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] idete na nešto, onda idete na ove kulturološke stvari.

1955
01:26:38,199 --> 01:26:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, Turska radi slično.

1956
01:26:40,199 --> 01:26:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da, danas se kolonije osvaja ne više vojskom,

1957
01:26:43,119 --> 01:26:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] nego glazbom, kulturom, financijama,

1958
01:26:46,619 --> 01:26:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] naravno koje su uvijek u Pozdodini,

1959
01:26:47,920 --> 01:26:49,520
[SPEAKER_00] na ove su ofici siljani način.

1960
01:26:49,520 --> 01:26:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] I to rade Mađari,

1961
01:26:50,739 --> 01:26:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nam rade svi,

1962
01:26:51,579 --> 01:26:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] od Indonezije do, ne znam, od Malezije.

1963
01:26:54,119 --> 01:26:55,859
[SPEAKER_01] Spomenula sam, malo Turci,

1964
01:26:55,859 --> 01:26:57,600
[SPEAKER_01] sve su jači Poljaci,

1965
01:26:57,600 --> 01:26:59,600
[SPEAKER_01] koji bi htjeli malo postati...

1966
01:26:59,600 --> 01:27:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi možemo hraniti

1967
01:27:02,039 --> 01:27:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] nekakvi 30-50 milijuna,

1968
01:27:04,060 --> 01:27:05,939
[SPEAKER_00] tako kažu neki naši makroekonomisti,

1969
01:27:05,939 --> 01:27:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali mi pecivo, dakle, smrznuto

1970
01:27:09,539 --> 01:27:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] i pekarski proizvodi, dakle,

1971
01:27:11,699 --> 01:27:13,020
[SPEAKER_00] proizvode se od, ne znam,

1972
01:27:13,020 --> 01:27:15,479
[SPEAKER_00] kojih žita u Poljskoj.

1973
01:27:15,479 --> 01:27:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mjesece dolaze ovdje,

1974
01:27:17,119 --> 01:27:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] tako da smo ostali bez pekarske suverenosti.

1975
01:27:20,880 --> 01:27:24,279
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nadam se da samo ne od ozračenog žita.

1976
01:27:24,279 --> 01:27:26,699
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo, nitko ne postavlja pitanje

1977
01:27:26,699 --> 01:27:28,600
[SPEAKER_01] tog, ta cest zagađene

1978
01:27:28,600 --> 01:27:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] krenjske zemlje.

1979
01:27:29,600 --> 01:27:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu kvalitete, mi smo potpuno,

1980
01:27:30,399 --> 01:27:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] tu da opće ne govorimo.

1981
01:27:32,000 --> 01:27:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] To bi mogli posebno i mislije,

1982
01:27:33,359 --> 01:27:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] to je već prije ovaj Plenkovića odrađeno,

1983
01:27:36,100 --> 01:27:37,520
[SPEAKER_00] gdje su tvrtke poput Agrogora,

1984
01:27:37,520 --> 01:27:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] koja je još dobro stajala,

1985
01:27:38,420 --> 01:27:40,340
[SPEAKER_00] zbog kontrole kvalitete,

1986
01:27:40,340 --> 01:27:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] imali ste nekakve, opet, korumpirane,

1987
01:27:43,460 --> 01:27:44,979
[SPEAKER_00] ali bar i državne ustanoje.

1988
01:27:44,979 --> 01:27:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, već je tada,

1989
01:27:46,260 --> 01:27:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] dakle prije Plenkovića,

1990
01:27:47,199 --> 01:27:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam koje godine,

1991
01:27:48,380 --> 01:27:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] zakon je to da sve te velike tvrtke

1992
01:27:51,260 --> 01:27:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] koje uvoze hranu,

1993
01:27:52,220 --> 01:27:53,479
[SPEAKER_00] dakle imaju svoje laboratorije.

1994
01:27:53,479 --> 01:27:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možete misliti kako,

1995
01:27:54,960 --> 01:27:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] to bolje da ga nemaju.

1996
01:27:56,960 --> 01:28:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, sad da ja malo prema vama nastupim,

1997
01:28:01,579 --> 01:28:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] da sumiramo na kraju 25-ta,

1998
01:28:04,739 --> 01:28:06,779
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno barim prva polovica 25-te,

1999
01:28:06,779 --> 01:28:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] da vas čujem.

2000
01:28:08,300 --> 01:28:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatska, Europa, svijet.

2001
01:28:11,699 --> 01:28:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] Što možemo očekivati?

2002
01:28:13,380 --> 01:28:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa Hrvatska na prvom mjestu.

2003
01:28:15,079 --> 01:28:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Trump je dao ovaj formulu

2004
01:28:17,420 --> 01:28:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] koja je, rekao bih, vječna.

2005
01:28:19,220 --> 01:28:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo se morate baviti sami sa sobom.

2006
01:28:22,680 --> 01:28:25,399
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, urediti Hrvatsku nije problem.

2007
01:28:25,399 --> 01:28:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, imamo resurse,

2008
01:28:26,840 --> 01:28:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] imamo geopolitički položaj,

2009
01:28:28,239 --> 01:28:30,159
[SPEAKER_00] imamo socijalni kapital,

2010
01:28:30,159 --> 01:28:32,560
[SPEAKER_00] imamo u cijelom zapadnom svijetu,

2011
01:28:32,560 --> 01:28:35,239
[SPEAKER_00] imamo nevjerovatnu dijasporu,

2012
01:28:35,239 --> 01:28:37,140
[SPEAKER_00] jedno veliko Hrvatsko srce.

2013
01:28:37,140 --> 01:28:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kad bi se samo to po određenim modelima

2014
01:28:39,960 --> 01:28:41,479
[SPEAKER_00] integracijskima uspostavilo,

2015
01:28:41,479 --> 01:28:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] da ne govorim,

2016
01:28:45,460 --> 01:28:46,560
[SPEAKER_00] mediteranske druge zemlje,

2017
01:28:46,560 --> 01:28:48,359
[SPEAKER_00] koje su sve svoje iseljeništvo

2018
01:28:48,359 --> 01:28:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] u suvremenim globalizacijskim okolonsima

2019
01:28:50,039 --> 01:28:52,399
[SPEAKER_00] pretvorili u golemu komparativnu prednost.

2020
01:28:52,399 --> 01:28:53,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, imate svoje ljude,

2021
01:28:53,699 --> 01:28:55,899
[SPEAKER_00] trgovce, diplomate, poslovnjake,

2022
01:28:55,899 --> 01:28:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, imate diljen svijeta.

2023
01:28:57,439 --> 01:28:58,840
[SPEAKER_00] To samo treba umrižiti.

2024
01:28:58,840 --> 01:29:01,479
[SPEAKER_00] A sve je topla voda.

2025
01:29:01,479 --> 01:29:04,100
[SPEAKER_01] Da, samo se čini da nema Trumpa,

2026
01:29:04,100 --> 01:29:04,760
[SPEAKER_01] barim našeg.

2027
01:29:04,760 --> 01:29:08,600
[SPEAKER_01] Najgore ako ga muka stvori.

2028
01:29:08,600 --> 01:29:13,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ponovno, danas je ključna riječ podcasta muka.

2029
01:29:13,479 --> 01:29:16,659
[SPEAKER_01] Muka koja dolazi.

2030
01:29:16,659 --> 01:29:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] To ste rekli za Hrvatsku.

2031
01:29:18,859 --> 01:29:20,659
[SPEAKER_01] Europa, bit će tu svega.

2032
01:29:20,659 --> 01:29:22,640
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan sugovornik, Larry St. Johnson,

2033
01:29:22,640 --> 01:29:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] mi je rekao da je ono, Europa...

2034
01:29:24,500 --> 01:29:26,520
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Europa izumire.

2035
01:29:26,520 --> 01:29:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] Europa nema sirovine,

2036
01:29:27,880 --> 01:29:29,399
[SPEAKER_00] nema energiju.

2037
01:29:29,399 --> 01:29:31,319
[SPEAKER_00] Najzagađeniji je kontinent.

2038
01:29:33,319 --> 01:29:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, na što može...

2039
01:29:34,300 --> 01:29:36,359
[SPEAKER_00] Davno je prestala biti kolonija,

2040
01:29:36,359 --> 01:29:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali sila i moć.

2041
01:29:37,119 --> 01:29:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da će najveći pobjednik biti

2042
01:29:40,579 --> 01:29:43,600
[SPEAKER_01] ipak gospodin Donald Trump.

2043
01:29:43,600 --> 01:29:45,779
[SPEAKER_00] I on ima ove muke,

2044
01:29:45,779 --> 01:29:47,479
[SPEAKER_00] a to je bijela smrti.

2045
01:29:47,479 --> 01:29:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] Život uvijek pobjeđuje.

2046
01:29:49,659 --> 01:29:51,020
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ne možemo.

2047
01:29:51,020 --> 01:29:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, još ćete doći,

2048
01:29:53,960 --> 01:29:55,180
[SPEAKER_01] još ćemo mi analizirati.

2049
01:29:55,180 --> 01:29:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki put je s vama zanimljivo.

2050
01:29:57,619 --> 01:29:58,060
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam.

2051
01:29:58,060 --> 01:29:58,939
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam.

2052
01:29:58,939 --> 01:30:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] Profesor Josip Jurčević

2053
01:30:01,760 --> 01:30:04,300
[SPEAKER_01] bio je gost ovog podcasta Mrežnica.

2054
01:30:04,300 --> 01:30:05,819
[SPEAKER_01] Vidimo se mi vrlo brzo.

